
The chakra folder contain elements to wrap compass project with python


curently only parts of carma context and carma objects are available


In order to compile, environment variable required:
    path to compass: COMPASS_ROOT_DIR 
    path to cuda   : CUDA_ROOT

The compilation is done with the command:
    python setup.py build_ext --inplace

    REQUIREMENT:
        * cython
        * python 2.7

To clean the folder, use the command:
    python clean.py


Content
    * wrapper sources:
            wrapper_chakra.pyx
            wrapper_chakra_type.pyx
            wrapper_chakra_context.pyx
            wrapper_chakra_obj.pyx.in
            wrapper_chakra_host_obj.pyx.in
            wrapper_magma.pyx.in
            wrapper_chakra_streams.pyx
    * process_tmpl.py             template management
    * setup.py                    compilation setups
    * clean.py                    cleaning script
    * test                        directory containing small python test codes
